## üöÄ Practical Tips for Your Transition

‚úî **Cloud mindset over engine differences:** Crunchy Bridge‚Äôs value is in automation, reliability, and tooling ‚Äî the core SQL and engine behaviour is still Postgres.
‚úî **Understand provider quirks:** Compare how Bridge handles auth/roles, backups, and scaling versus your Aurora experience.
‚úî **Join the community:** Crunchy Data has tutorials, Slack/Discord communities, and blog posts that keep you connected to real use-cases and patterns. ([Crunchy Data][4])

